{"tid":90321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[免費]招集所有下決心想密集式學日文既巴打","createTime":"2017-01-22T04:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T11:07:22.000Z","uid":58273,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c85c2ca6061aa26b218f41129304bc3459bc209c","tid":90321,"uid":58273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"事原有個巴打免費教日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://forum2.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum2.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype&d=BdHwqxikkEz9Gr0EJgk6d5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=ec30fc6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum2.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type</a> ST message 6612897 <br />\n由於反應熱烈所以租左個地方教, <br />\n但有D人就三分鐘熱度返下唔返下,而且都係一個星期一堂 <br />\n咁我同果個巴打傾過,我完全唔識由0開始想一星期密集式咁學得唔得 <br />\n佢話冇問題,但最好多幾個一齊同唔係玩玩下既 <br />\n所以宜家我想搵幾個有心學既巴打一齊去學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於宜家一至五6:45-8:15都有堂所以我同果位巴打傾左2個時間 <br />\n地點:大角咀 <br />\n時間:一星期四至五日,A:4:30~6:6:30,B:8:30~10:30 <br />\n有興趣既可以留TG/LINE,集合左之後再商量確實時間,希望可以過左年開班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d23664d1167fdfc5d91073500a657a17d786f28","tid":90321,"uid":58273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:09:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9415fd39c25281f2d0f062baebd281e15c4d7c0b","tid":90321,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:13:00.000Z","msg":"telegram : swaggerrrrs<br />\n暑期去日本逗留一個月<br />\n呢排重諗緊自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26d0d196be9a618f4f12f84edb67232421c3690","tid":90321,"uid":1918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:10:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"7423a9bd82ee711d16c87f657d1ef34eb97bce6b","tid":90321,"uid":1918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</block